      • addTagButtonClicked

        public void addTagButtonClicked()
        Method to call when "Add" Tag button is clicked. Shows the add tag dialog.

      • deleteTagButtonClicked

        public void deleteTagButtonClicked()
        Method to call when "Delete" Tag button is clicked. Deletes selected Tag, does nothing if no selection is made.

      • moveButtonClicked

        public void moveButtonClicked()
        Method to call when "Move to..." button is clicked. Does nothing if no album is selected from the combo box. Checks if the move was successful, will transition to either the photo window or slideshow window depending on if the photo moved was the last photo in the album.

      • captionButtonClicked

        public void captionButtonClicked()
        Method to call when the "Change Caption" button is clicked. Shows a dialog to edit the photo's caption.
